  <section class="update">
    <div class="update-date">
      Jun <b class="d-block">2022</b>
    </div>
    <p>
      <b>Simple dashboard:</b> Diabetes reports are now available for dashboard users in regions where blood sugar measures are being taken. Users can view DM registrations, follow-ups, missed visits and lost to follow-up for patients with diabetes. If your region does not use the diabetes feature, please talk to your leadership team and Simple team about enabling it.
    </p>
  </section>
